definition:
Someone descended from Sered who was a man of the tribe of Zebulun living at the time of Egypt and Wilderness, first mentioned at Gen.46.14; 
 son of: Zebulun (H2074); 
 brother of: Elon (H0356H) and Jahleel (H3177)
Group of se.red (סֶ֫רֶד "Sered" H5624) 
 § Sardites, of Sered "fright"
 descendants of Sered, the 1st born son of Zebulun
